1.安装redis扩展
$ pip3 install redis

2.安装mysql.connector扩展
$ sudo apt-get install python3-mysql.connector
或者
$ sudo pip3.6 install mysql-connector-python
# http://blog.topspeedsnail.com/archives/6018
# Centos
$ /usr/local/python3.5/bin/python3 -m pip install mysql-connector-python

3.安装kafka-python扩展
$ sudo pip3 install kafka-python

4.安装requests扩展
$ sudo pip3 install requests

5.安装confluent-kafka-python,参考： 
https://github.com/confluentinc/confluent-kafka-python

7.安装pymongo
$ sudo python3 -m pip install pymongo
或
$ sudo pip3 install pymongo

8.安装dateutil模块
$ sudo python3 -m pip install python-dateutil

9.安装pyssdb模块(仅支持Python:2.6,2.7,3.5,3.6)
$ sudo python3.5 -m pip install pyssdbA
